skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: keeping it real
des: Listen to the latest talks from Keeping It Real With Dr. Linda Chinn. Dr. Chinn believes in Keeping Real Not Religious. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next".
